    <title>SAP Build &amp; Integration Suite CodeJams in Dubai in March 2025</title>
    <updated>2025-02-12T08:22:45.035000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>eshrinivasan</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/148298</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hello SAP Community Dubai,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;For the first time in Dubai, SAP is conducting two CodeJams on &lt;STRONG&gt;Integration Suite&lt;/STRONG&gt; and &lt;STRONG&gt;SAP Build&lt;/STRONG&gt; topics. These events are hosted by &lt;STRONG&gt;Mark9 Solutions&lt;/STRONG&gt; and &lt;STRONG&gt;Robert Bosch&lt;/STRONG&gt; respectively. These are &lt;STRONG&gt;free&lt;/STRONG&gt;, &lt;STRONG&gt;full day,&lt;/STRONG&gt; &lt;STRONG&gt;hands on&lt;/STRONG&gt; events on BTP topics for enabling users on the tools and technologies related to Integration Suite and SAP Build. More details on these events and how to register are provided in the links below.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;March 25, 2025&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1831859487"&gt;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/sap-codejam-connecting-systems-and-services-using-sap-integration-suite/ev-p/14007747" target="_self"&gt;&lt;FONT size="3"&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":united_arab_emirates:"&gt;🇦🇪&lt;/span&gt;SAP CodeJam: Connecting systems and services using SAP Integration Suite&amp;nbsp;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;March 26, 2025&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1635345982"&gt;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/sap-build-create-business-apps-and-processes-without-code-dubai-uae/ev-p/14014842" target="_self"&gt;&lt;FONT size="3"&gt;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":united_arab_emirates:"&gt;🇦🇪&lt;/span&gt;SAP Build: Create Business Apps and Processes Without Code&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT size="3"&gt;CC:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/107"&gt;@ajmaradiaga&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Join, Learn, Collaborate and Network!&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam-discussions/sap-build-amp-integration-suite-codejams-in-dubai-in-march-2025/td-p/14014880"/>
